{
  "info": {
    "name": "EventLedger Demo",
    "description": "End-to-end demo of Event Ledger.\n\n**Run order:** Execute folders A → B → C top to bottom. Folders D (Swagger), E (observability), and F (graceful degradation) are optional. **Folder F requires A first.**\n\n**Services**\n- Gateway (public): http://localhost:8080\n- Account Service (debug/demo): http://localhost:8081\n\n**Start**\n```powershell\ndocker compose down -v && docker compose up --build\n```\nOr run both .NET projects locally on 8080/8081.\n\n**Fresh demo:** Reset volumes (`docker compose down -v`) or delete local `gateway.db` / `account.db` before re-running — fixed eventIds return **200** (replay) instead of **201** on repeat.\n\n**Status codes (Gateway POST /events)**\n- 201 Created — first submission of an eventId\n- 200 OK — idempotent replay (`Idempotency-Replay: true`)\n- 400 — validation error\n- 429 — inbound rate/concurrency limit\n- 503 — Account Service down (event not stored)\n\n**Resiliency**\n- Inbound: concurrency bulkhead + per-client write rate limit\n- Outbound: Polly circuit breaker → retry (jitter) → timeout\n\n**Graceful degradation (folder F)**\n1. `docker compose stop account-service`\n2. POST /events → 503; GET /events still serves Gateway local data; balance GET fails (connection refused)\n3. `docker compose start account-service`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "gatewayUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "accountUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8081" },
    { "key": "accountId", "value": "acct-demo-001" },
    { "key": "creditEventId", "value": "evt-credit-1001" },
    { "key": "debitEventId", "value": "evt-debit-1002" },
    { "key": "outOfOrderAcct", "value": "acct-demo-out-of-order" },
    { "key": "degradeEventId", "value": "evt-degrade-001" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "A. Happy path",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "0a. Health - Gateway",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{gatewayUrl}}/health"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "0b. Health - Account Service",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{accountUrl}}/health"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "1. Submit CREDIT (+150.00)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Created (201) or replayed (200)', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect([200, 201]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"eventId\": \"{{creditEventId}}\",\n  \"accountId\": \"{{accountId}}\",\n  \"type\": \"CREDIT\",\n  \"amount\": 150.00,\n  \"currency\": \"USD\",\n  \"eventTimestamp\": \"2026-06-26T16:00:00Z\",\n  \"metadata\": { \"source\": \"demo\", \"note\": \"opening deposit\" }\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{gatewayUrl}}/events"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Submit DEBIT (40.00, type=DEBIT)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Created (201) or replayed (200)', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect([200, 201]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"eventId\": \"{{debitEventId}}\",\n  \"accountId\": \"{{accountId}}\",\n  \"type\": \"DEBIT\",\n  \"amount\": 40.00,\n  \"currency\": \"USD\",\n  \"eventTimestamp\": \"2026-06-26T16:05:00Z\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{gatewayUrl}}/events"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Idempotency replay (same CREDIT)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Replay returns 200', function () {",
                  "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Idempotency-Replay header is true', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect(pm.response.headers.get('Idempotency-Replay')).to.eql('true');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"eventId\": \"{{creditEventId}}\",\n  \"accountId\": \"{{accountId}}\",\n  \"type\": \"CREDIT\",\n  \"amount\": 150.00,\n  \"currency\": \"USD\",\n  \"eventTimestamp\": \"2026-06-26T16:00:00Z\",\n  \"metadata\": { \"source\": \"demo\", \"note\": \"opening deposit\" }\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{gatewayUrl}}/events"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Get event by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{gatewayUrl}}/events/{{creditEventId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "5. List events for account",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{gatewayUrl}}/events?account={{accountId}}",
              "host": ["{{gatewayUrl}}"],
              "path": ["events"],
              "query": [{ "key": "account", "value": "{{accountId}}" }]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "6. Get balance (expect 110.00)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Balance is 110.00', function () {",
                  "  var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(json.balance).to.eql(110);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{accountUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}/balance"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "7. Get account detail",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{accountUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
